+{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01821DUnaBtqjoNSb5PFMsAn","type":"tool_result","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Perfect! Here's a comprehensive overview of the workspace:\n\n## Project Structure Overview\n\nThe workspace contains a TypeScript project for a **multi-tenant analytics dashboard API**. The directory structure is:\n\n```\n/workspace\n├── .git/\n├── .thunderdome/\n├── src/                     (empty, contains only .gitkeep)\n├── dist/                    (compiled output, will be generated)\n├── node_modules/            (dependencies)\n├── .eslintrc.cjs\n├── .gitignore\n├── TASK.md\n├── package.json\n├── package-lock.json\n├── schema.sql\n├── tsconfig.json\n├── vitest.config.ts\n└── .thunderdome-output.jsonl\n```\n\n## Key Files Contents\n\n### 1. **package.json**\n```json\n{\n  \"name\": \"bench-analytics-dashboard\",\n  \"version\": \"1.0.0\",\n  \"description\": \"T8: Multi-tenant analytics dashboard benchmark\",\n  \"main\": \"dist/app.js\",\n  \"scripts\": {\n    \"build\": \"tsc\",\n    \"lint\": \"eslint src/\",\n    \"test\": \"vitest run\"\n  },\n  \"devDependencies\": {\n    \"@typescript-eslint/eslint-plugin\": \"^7.0.0\",\n    \"@typescript-eslint/parser\": \"^7.0.0\",\n    \"eslint\": \"^8.56.0\",\n    \"typescript\": \"^5.4.0\",\n    \"@vitest/coverage-v8\": \"^2.0.0\",\n    \"vitest\": \"^2.0.0\",\n    \"supertest\": \"^7.0.0\",\n    \"@types/express\": \"^4.17.21\",\n    \"@types/better-sqlite3\": \"^7.6.8\",\n    \"@types/jsonwebtoken\": \"^9.0.0\",\n    \"@types/supertest\": \"^6.0.0\",\n    \"@types/uuid\": \"^10.0.0\"\n  },\n  \"dependencies\": {\n    \"express\": \"^4.18.0\",\n    \"better-sqlite3\": \"^11.0.0\",\n    \"jsonwebtoken\": \"^9.0.0\",\n    \"uuid\": \"^10.0.0\"\n  }\n}\n```\n\n### 2. **tsconfig.json**\n```json\n{\n  \"compilerOptions\": {\n    \"strict\": true,\n    \"target\": \"ES2022\",\n    \"module\": \"Node16\",\n    \"moduleResolution\": \"Node16\",\n    \"outDir\": \"./dist\",\n    \"rootDir\": \"./src\",\n    \"esModuleInterop\": true,\n    \"forceConsistentCasingInFileNames\": true,\n    \"skipLibCheck\": true,\n    \"declaration\": true\n  },\n  \"include\": [\"src/**/*\"],\n  \"exclude\": [\"node_modules\", \"dist\", \"tests\"]\n}\n```\n\n### 3. **schema.sql**\n```sql\n-- Multi-tenant analytics dashboard schema\nCREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS users (\n  id TEXT PRIMARY KEY,\n  email TEXT NOT NULL UNIQUE,\n  password_hash TEXT NOT NULL,\n  tenant_id TEXT NOT NULL,\n  role TEXT NOT NULL DEFAULT 'viewer' CHECK(role IN ('admin', 'viewer', 'editor')),\n  created_at TEXT NOT NULL DEFAULT (datetime('now'))\n);\n\nCREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS events (\n  id TEXT PRIMARY KEY,\n  tenant_id TEXT NOT NULL,\n  name TEXT NOT NULL,\n  properties TEXT NOT NULL DEFAULT '{}',\n  timestamp TEXT NOT NULL DEFAULT (datetime('now')),\n  user_id TEXT,\n  session_id TEXT\n);\n\nCREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS dashboards (\n  id TEXT PRIMARY KEY,\n  tenant_id TEXT NOT NULL,\n  name TEXT NOT NULL,\n  owner_id TEXT NOT NULL,\n  config TEXT NOT NULL DEFAULT '{}',\n  created_at TEXT NOT NULL DEFAULT (datetime('now')),\n  updated_at TEXT NOT NULL DEFAULT (datetime('now')),\n  FOREIGN KEY (owner_id) REFERENCES users(id)\n);\n\nCREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS widgets (\n  id TEXT PRIMARY KEY,\n  dashboard_id TEXT NOT NULL,\n  type TEXT NOT NULL CHECK(type IN ('counter', 'timeseries', 'breakdown', 'funnel')),\n  config TEXT NOT NULL DEFAULT '{}',\n  position_x INTEGER NOT NULL DEFAULT 0,\n  position_y INTEGER NOT NULL DEFAULT 0,\n  width INTEGER NOT NULL DEFAULT 1,\n  height INTEGER NOT NULL DEFAULT 1,\n  FOREIGN KEY (dashboard_id) REFERENCES dashboards(id) ON DELETE CASCADE\n);\n\nCREATE INDEX IF NOT EXISTS idx_events_tenant ON events(tenant_id);\nCREATE INDEX IF NOT EXISTS idx_events_name ON events(name);\nCREATE INDEX IF NOT EXISTS idx_events_timestamp ON events(timestamp);\nCREATE INDEX IF NOT EXISTS idx_dashboards_tenant ON dashboards(tenant_id);\nCREATE INDEX IF NOT EXISTS idx_users_tenant ON users(tenant_id);\n```\n\n### 4. **.eslintrc.cjs**\n```javascript\nmodule.exports = {\n  parser: '@typescript-eslint/parser',\n  plugins: ['@typescript-eslint'],\n  extends: ['plugin:@typescript-eslint/recommended'],\n  parserOptions: {\n    ecmaVersion: 2022,\n    sourceType: 'module',\n  },\n  rules: {\n    '@typescript-eslint/no-unused-vars': [\n      'error',\n      { argsIgnorePattern: '^_', varsIgnorePattern: '^_' },\n    ],\n  },\n};\n```\n\n### 5. **vitest.config.ts**\n```typescript\nimport { defineConfig } from 'vitest/config';\n\nexport default defineConfig({\n  test: {\n    globals: true,\n    testTimeout: 10000,\n  },\n});\n```\n\n### 6. **TASK.md** (Complete Requirements)\n\n**Category:** greenfield/complex\n**Timeout:** 30 minutes\n\n#### Objective\nBuild a multi-tenant analytics dashboard API in TypeScript. All source code goes in `src/`.\n\n#### Requirements\n\nThe system needs five core capabilities:\n\n1. **User Management** - Register accounts, log in, receive JWT tokens. Support roles (admin, editor, viewer). Admins can change other users' roles. Users can view their own profile.\n\n2. **Data Ingestion** - Authenticated users send analytics events (name, properties, timestamp). Support single events and batches. Events auto-associate with user's tenant.\n\n3. **Query Engine** - Analyze collected event data with:\n   - Counting events matching a filter\n   - Timeseries queries (bucket counts over time)\n   - Breakdowns (group by property value)\n   - All queries must respect tenant isolation\n\n4. **Dashboard Configuration** - Create, read, update, delete dashboards. Dashboards are named collections belonging to a tenant.\n\n5. **Data Export** - Export event data in CSV and JSON formats. Dashboard data also exportable. Must respect tenant boundaries.\n\n#### Technical Requirements\n- Use SQLite for persistence (schema.sql provided)\n- Use JWT tokens for authentication\n- All tenant-data routes require authentication\n- Export `createApp` function from `src/index.ts` or `src/app.ts` returning Express instance\n- Unauthenticated requests to protected routes receive 401 status\n\n#### Validation\n- `npm run build` - TypeScript compilation\n- `npm run lint` - Code quality\n- Write your own tests to verify implementation\n\n#### Constraints\n- All code in `src/` directory\n- Must compile with provided tsconfig.json (strict mode, ES2022, Node16)\n- Must pass ESLint configuration\n- Use provided schema.sql\n- Dependencies: express, better-sqlite3, jsonwebtoken, uuid\n\n## Summary\n\n- **src/ directory**: Currently empty (only contains `.gitkeep`)\n- **No existing source files**: You need to build the entire API from scratch\n- **No existing tests**: Test files need to be created\n- **Technology Stack**: Express.js, SQLite, JWT, TypeScript\n- **Build scripts**: `npm run build` (tsc), `npm run lint` (eslint), `npm run test` (vitest)"},{"type":"text","text":"agentId: afdc864 (for resuming to continue this agent's work if needed)\n<usage>total_tokens: 16384\ntool_uses: 9\nduration_ms: 21338</usage>"}]}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"e6f729fa-b4ee-444d-a100-7dff85710c4e","uuid":"2afda88f-f703-4313-8ea2-1f34bd64d082","tool_use_result":{"status":"completed","prompt":"Explore the /workspace directory thoroughly. I need to understand:\n1. The full project structure (all files and directories)\n2. The contents of package.json (dependencies, scripts)\n3. The contents of tsconfig.json\n4. The contents of schema.sql\n5. Any existing source files in src/\n6. The contents of eslint config\n7. Any existing test files\n8. The TASK.md contents\n\nRead all these files and report their full contents back to me.","agentId":"afdc864","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Perfect! Here's a comprehensive overview of the workspace:\n\n## Project Structure Overview\n\nThe workspace contains a TypeScript project for a **multi-tenant analytics dashboard API**. The directory structure is:\n\n```\n/workspace\n├── .git